=== Level 40–80: Battlestaves ===
{{plinkp|Celastrus bark}} Fletching [[Battlestaff|Battlestaves]] requires one piece of [[Celastrus bark]], and yields 80 experience per bark. Only level 40 is needed to fletch a battlestaff, which makes it a better training method than fletching bows in this level range. At level 80, the player can fletch magic shortbows which yields more xp per action.

* Experience needed: 1,948,844
* [[Celastrus bark]]s needed: 24,361
* Time: 17 hours 40 minutes
** Experience rate: 110k xp/hr
* Celastrus barks cost = {{Coins|{{GEP|Celastrus bark|24361}}}}
* Battlestaves = {{Coins|{{GEP|Battlestaff|24361}}}}
** Total Profit/Loss = {{Coins|{{GEP|Battlestaff|24361}}-{{GEP|Celastrus bark|24361}}}}
*** Per xp = {{Coins|({{GEP|Battlestaff}}-{{GEP|Celastrus bark}})/80}}

===Level 92–99: Redwood shields===
{{plinkp|Redwood shield}} [[Redwood shield]]s are an alternative method to fletching bows. Fletching one shield requires two redwood logs, and gives 216 experience per shield.

*Experience needed: 6,517,178
*[[Redwood logs]] needed: 60,346
*Time: 38 hours 35 minutes
**Experience rate: 168k xp/hr
*Redwood logs cost = {{Coins|{{GEP|Redwood logs|60346}}}}
*Redwood shields = {{Coins|{{GEP|Redwood shield|30173}}}}
**Total Profit/Loss(fletching) = {{Coins|{{GEP|Redwood shield|30173}}-{{GEP|Redwood logs|60346}}}}
***Per xp = {{Coins|({{GEP|Redwood shield}}-{{GEP|Redwood logs|2}})/216}}

